snippet: Gunmen killed 14 people in Nukhaib, a police official said. An official in Karbala, where several of the dead were from, said that the assailants had stopped the travelers at a fake checkpoint.
abstract: Iraqi police say gunmen killed 14 people in Nukhaib after stopping travelers at fake checkpoint.
lead_paragraph: Gunmen killed 14 people in Nukhaib, a police official said. An official in Karbala, where several of the dead were from, said that the assailants had stopped the travelers at a fake checkpoint.

headline.main: Iraq: 14 Travelers Are Killed by Gunmen
headline.print_headline: Iraq: 14 Travelers Are Killed by Gunmen
